  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4573868">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4573868/" class="title-link">出色的传记</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4573868"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/xyzlsh/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1866314-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/xyzlsh/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">要追寻不要躲避</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-01-10"
      class="main-meta">2011-01-10 23:31:16</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4573868_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  此书有日本人的特点，重视细节描述，即使这些细节与山本五十六这个主题并不是很相关。譬如，讲山本喜欢用女佣人用过的洗澡水洗澡，喜欢背女人等。 山本还在上世纪30年代就验证过“水变油”的实验。 此外，没想到日本陆海军的矛盾如此的严重，竟然发展到海军省不信任陆军派来的...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4573868_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4573868_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





